</p></section><section id="GUID-1156E15C-FA11-42F7-80CE-F9823F371FA9" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Function</title><p class="- topic/p ">Expire date of the ink in the ink tanks (C, M, Y, K or W). 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">This value is updated every time new ink is added into the ink tank. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Example: 119;6;30 = July 30 2019 (Month start at 0!). 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> The SDS parameter shows the date when the expiry state will be set to 'Almost expired'. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">A warning is displayed on the operator panel. In case no further action is done, the expiry state will change to 'Expired' in 28 days from this day. 
